node.text: Encourage a growth mindset in your classroom this back to school 🌱 🧠 This fun activity pack from Dana's Wonderland includes reading comprehension passages, a growth mindset motto, information on the power of yet, coloring pages and more. This resource also includes a ready-to-use interactive activity students can complete on any device through Easel by TpT.  Download via the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Teachers Pay Teachers on July 28, 2021 tagging @lololoveslearning, and @theteachingflowers. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
"Growing up, school was my sanctuary. My classrooms were my safe spaces. I have grown such a heart and compassion for children and believe they deserve every bit of innocence and childhood to which they’re entitled. It is for this reason why I chose Elementary Education: because I know teachers are much more than just teachers." - @theteachingflowers. 

Download this free 'Why I Teach" printable by @lololoveslearning on TpT via the link in our bio 🎒✏️📚🖌️
